latestIgtvVideos.title: Artis Phantom Silks Skincare Primer✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’m OBSESSED with the @byartis Phantom Silks Skincare Primer because of how glowy and hydrated it made my skin!! #sponsored 
This primer is meant to hold in all your skincare and hydrate your skin with the Hyaluronic Acid🤩 This is now a go-to of mine for my Roy time & self-care!! Also, the Elite Oval 6 brush is absolutely amazing for skincare & makeup! It was so easy to blend the moisturizer into my skin👏🏽 Next time, I will make sure to put the moisturizer on my face and not on the brush! Cannot wait to keep using these products & you can use code ASHA20 for 20% off at checkout! Y’all are gonna looove these products!!🤍
